    "When we compared YOLOv5's original and the proposed model, we found that the proposed model performed better.",
    "Figure 6 shows the proposed model's results, which include 97.7% SEN, 94.9% SPC, 96.3% PPV, 97.2% ACC, and 92.8% MCC value.",
    "The original YOLOv5, in contrast, obtained 92% SEN, 91.6% PPV, 91.8% ACC, and 85.4% MCC value.",
    "We further evaluated the performance of three models (InceptionV3, EfficientNet, Table 6.",
    "The model evaluation of different grades for glioma brain tumor."
